Usage: sdwan.py device [OPTIONS]

  Display, Download, and View CLI Config for Devices.

  Returns information about each device that is part of the fabric.

  Example command:

      ./sdwan.py device

      ./sdwan.py device --config deviceID

      ./sdwan.py device --csv deviceID | all

      ./sdwan.py device --detach deviceID

      ./sdwan.py device --download deviceID | all

      ./sdwan.py device --invalid deviceID

      ./sdwan.py device --template deviceID

      ./sdwan.py device --valid deviceID

      ./sdwan.py device --variable deviceID

Options:
  --config TEXT    Print Device CLI Configuration
  --csv TEXT       Output Device Variables to CSV
  --detach TEXT    Detach Device from Device Template
  --download TEXT  Download Device CLI Configuration
  --invalid TEXT   Make Device Certificate Invalid"
  --template TEXT  Display Device Template
  --variable TEXT  Display Device Variable and Values
  --valid TEXT     Make Device Certificate Valid"
  --help           Show this message and exit.
